      "Title": "Invex.RepoUtils.Atom.Module.Helpers.IApiSurfaceHelper",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Invex.RepoUtils.Atom.Module.Helpers.IApiSurfaceHelper.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Provides functionality for analyzing the public API surface of the repository by diffing the\ntracked API definition files between two commits, and classifying the resulting changes as\neither major (removals) or minor (additions) breaking changes.</p>\n"
