      "Title": "Invex.RepoUtils.Atom.Module.Helpers.IDocFxHelper",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Invex.RepoUtils.Atom.Module.Helpers.IDocFxHelper.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Provides functionality for generating, serving, and publishing\n<a href=\"https://dotnet.github.io/docfx/\">DocFX</a> documentation for the repository.\nThe helper builds the static documentation site, can host it locally for previewing, and\npublishes the generated output to a project's <code>gh-pages</code> branch for GitHub Pages hosting.</p>\n"
    },
