      "Title": "Invex.RepoUtils.Atom.Module.Helpers.INugetPackageUnlistHelper",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/Invex.RepoUtils.Atom.Module.Helpers.INugetPackageUnlistHelper.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Provides functionality for discovering and unlisting prerelease packages that have been\nsuperseded by a newly published version. Versions are discovered through the NuGet flat-container\nAPI and unlisted via the feed's HTTP <code>DELETE</code> endpoint, with a summary written to the Atom\nbuild report.</p>\n"
    },
